kpi_info.use: The number of NRT DCH setup rejects for interactive traffic class due to power limits in UL. UPDATED: When admission control rejects interactive DCH setup due to power limits in UL. This counter includes initial DCH setups, handover attempts and channel type switches from E-DCH to DCH.
